                        <join result="offenceCrimeDate" targOrder="Y" targets="t18400406-1084-offence-1 t18400406-cd-61"></join>16th of March</rs>, 1 coal-scuttle, value 3<hi rend="italic">s</hi>., the goods of <persName id="t18400406-name-399" type="victimName">
